{"tid":2446934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北上港人疫情下回流淪「麥難民」無家者突破2,000人 　24年新高","createTime":"2021-03-14T23:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T11:31:07.000Z","uid":271829,"like":149,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"81bf262ed26dd260cc6383045d3df2fc53b881fd","tid":2446934,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iSlEto_USEZEA_oRAI8oMJeCQtY=/7360x4912/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4GPNLEDZXNDTXEJE33VVTRINLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiSlEto_USEZEA_oRAI8oMJeCQtY%3D%2F7360x4912%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4GPNLEDZXNDTXEJE33VVTRINLU.jpg&h=af1996dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年本港麥難民人數倍增，越來越多基層市民負擔不起屋租，只好在通宵營業的麥當勞留宿。（社協提供圖片，雷日昇攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1zX8spo21647NKxfol95j7NS6ZQ=/6000x4000/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DIKQEJAOOFBJDO7GTDEXMYVSRA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1zX8spo21647NKxfol95j7NS6ZQ%3D%2F6000x4000%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDIKQEJAOOFBJDO7GTDEXMYVSRA.JPG&h=6bb58ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年本港麥難民人數倍增，越來越多基層市民負擔不起屋租，只好在通宵營業的麥當勞留宿。（社協提供圖片，雷日昇攝）<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n一個社會進步還是倒退，走到街頭一看或有答案。截至去年底，社署已登記露宿者約有1,500人，是回歸以來有紀錄最多，但未計及沒登記人數，而且在武漢肺炎疫情下，逾25萬人失業。社區組織協會估計，目前全港無家者超過2,000人。<br />\n由商人治港，到公務員上場，梁振英的「港人港地」無疾而終，女特首稱號「好打得」卻對付不了地產霸權，香港地要瞓街的人越來越多，當政府叫人去大灣區生活，卻有港人因內地工廠倒閉，回流香港要淪落街頭；也有在疫情下回流的港人，因付擔不起屋租，一度寄居麥當勞。無家者背後都有一個故事，社協透過展覽把他們的困境記錄下來，盼喚起社會關注，促使政府制定無家者友善政策。<br />\n<br />\n東莞工廠結業回流香港 難覓住處慘變「麥難民」<br />\n「你見到出面住嘅人係越來越多。」阿明（化名）口中的「出面」，是指「瞓街」，可以是連接尖沙嘴文化中心的行人隧道，也可以是深水埗通州街公園，或是福華街通宵營業的麥當勞，「行過仲見到好多人喺度，如果有改善，應該嗰個族群越來越少」。他曾是那族群的一員，夜宿快餐店的麥難民。<br />\n阿明在東莞工作10多年，大約3年前任職的工廠結業，不得已回流香港，卻沒地方住，惟有做麥難民。後來經社工轉介，他住過幾間政府資助的露宿者宿位，但限時進出，僅可住半年。1年多前，他改住社區組織協會「友家宿舍」，24小時開放方便他找到一份運輸工作，年已半百，暫算安穩，「過返正常生活」。<br />\n有瓦遮頭沒人想「瞓街」，但阿明發現街上的無家者，比起他3年前初次露宿街頭時增加很多，「我覺得香港係冇進步，停留咗喺度，因為冇改善到」。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210315/CFRL4VDZKNAFDD24DKVV3HC5YQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2FCFRL4VDZKNAFDD24DKVV3HC5YQ%2F&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=a6792473\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2FCFRL4VDZKNAFDD24DKVV3HC5YQ%2F&h=cd777f7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210315/CFRL4VDZKNAFDD24DKVV3HC5YQ/</a>"},{"pid":"1a419d4f65b697007bc696f418ec183d1795674f","tid":2446934,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:04:25.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"102479182df2ba0c6a28930ce2129bedb620f94a","tid":2446934,"uid":155095,"like":140,"dislike":5,"score":135,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:05:24.000Z","msg":"點解唔去大灣區買樓呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2490000/2492063/061119prop_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2490000%2F2492063%2F061119prop_1024.jpg&h=a0c66fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2320000/2321938/great_bay_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2320000%2F2321938%2Fgreat_bay_1024.png&h=70ce25d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2495000/2498542/house_exmobile_20191115_J_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv